sources.title: Hunky & Spunky PizzaFLIX CARTOON SPECIAL
sources.description: Hunky & Spunky! The complete Technicolor Cartoon Collection featuring the Oscar Nominated debut Hunky And Spunky (1938), plus Always Kickin' (1939), The Barnyard Brat (1939), A Kick in Time (1940), Snubbed By A Snob (1940), You Can't Shoe A Horse Fly (1940), Vitamin Hay (1941), and Yankee Doodle Donkey (1944).
